Eyup, pal! I was just basking in awe
at the amazing thing we've achieved
here with this new school!

rows.label: tlk4730016802_msg0002

Reinforcing the walls and fixing leaks
in the roof together with the kids were
some real moments to be treasured...

Oof! I almost forgot, we've got new
faces now, don't we? Looks like it's
time for an extension then!
